{
  "stem": "2581.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So rather than wait and be beaten up, people delivered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's strange to picture this, but people delivered their possessions to the-- to the-- that office, wherever it was decided to.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At first, let me just go back a bit when we first moved into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was in contact with the peasants that were his customers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they would, like, wanted a suit turned from one side on the other, because there was no fabric.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was worn out on the sides or was turned out on there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were sitting in the attic and sewing it, because they took away all our machines.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was in that Judenrat, in that building, they had some machines that you could rent, but for an hour or two, what you needed for long seams, you know?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they would bring some food for that worker to eat it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But that lasted a short time, and they started to send people to work camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were no-- we didn't know about concentration camps, to Poznan and difference, [INAUDIBLE], I remember.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I was still too young for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they were people that didn't-- didn't have this job, these jobs that the Germans needed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So these people were-- constantly were sent out to work, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And of course, after awhile, we heard that other cities, other towns are being deported to the ghetto Lodz where we were, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember sitting on the second floor, and we heard these trucks rumble through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I looked out and I saw people standing on the trucks, and these were people from the city of [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Pabianice ?] taken to [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Chelmno ?] you know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "No, these are people from [POLISH] that were taken to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
